{"tid":2314382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國眾院料周一全體表決《香港人民自由與選擇法案》","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T14:26:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb1221a57572c0eafd1fa1408fba1381f26a094","tid":2314382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563843-20201206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563843-20201206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2mg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=7c0c059f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563843-20201206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3857083d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563843-20201206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會眾議院預料當地星期一，全體表決《香港人民自由與選擇法案》，若果獲通過，將送往參議院表決。<br />\n<br />\n由於法案被列為擱置辯論，即是不存在爭議，獲得最少三分二議員支持，立法過程進入快速通道，在全院的審議辯論限時40分鐘，不會有新的修正案。<br />\n<br />\n根據法案內容，美國政府會為已持有簽證並在美國，但返回香港後可能面臨政治迫害的港人，提供臨時保護身份，法案亦會加速處理為逃離政治迫害的香港居民赴美難民申請程序，並將這類申請，排除在美國每年整體難民接收人數限制以外。"},{"pid":"f6644ec2f47aaa02bc278971a090bca28fe99c8f","tid":2314382,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42c8cd5a649aa9d68cc5327d7ba353e2a10b5aa","tid":2314382,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:46:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>吓</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b5ab5086a53375a1f0b52550860220503fb1e21","tid":2314382,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"其實仲有冇用"},{"pid":"1a37316e11890f4aa8b4d81f02f012b56f023824","tid":2314382,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"要證明被迫害都唔會太多人<br />\n叫做有D野做下咁<br />\n大部份人要走都有渠道走"},{"pid":"b3c1370b6fe3184fdb06c9a8e3c9c74eba45b19c","tid":2314382,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"叫做多條路走<br />\n英加澳都唔岩咪去美國"},{"pid":"d9cd955719d00843814ca3ce654dadc1b0f40ae0","tid":2314382,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb2f8aff151ad14ff4e6ff75fc716b3a1941f99","tid":2314382,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"美國人真偉大<br />\n一蚊都無收過<br />\n都持續撐香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}